'''Mohammad Ali Hasan Abu Hashish''' ({{langx|ar|مُحَمَّد عَلِيّ حَسَن أَبُو حَشِيش}}; born 9 May 1995) is a professional footballer who plays as a [[left-back]] for [[Iraq Stars League]] side [[Al-Karma SC|Al-Karma]]. Born in Iraq, he represents the [[Jordan national football team|Jordan national team]].

==Career==
Abu Hashish began his senior career with the Jordanian club [[Al-Baqa'a SC|Al-Baqa'a]], before moving to [[Al-Salt SC|Al-Salt]] in 2020. On 1 February 2022, he moved to [[Al-Wehdat SC|Al-Wehdat]] and helped them win the [[2022 Jordanian Pro League]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://alanbatnews.net/article/354306|title=الوحدات يتعاقد مع أبو حشيش|date=January 2, 2022|website=الأنباط}}</ref> On 10 January 2023, he transferred to the Iraqi club [[Al-Zawraa SC|Al-Zawraa]] on a short-term contract.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ammonnews.net/article/735368|title=صحيفة عمون : سعادة وأبو حشيش يتفقان مع الزوراء العراقي|website=وكالة عمون الاخبارية}}</ref> On 10 July 2023 he moved to the Lebanese club [[Al Ahed FC|Al Ahed]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.kooora.com/?n=1253578|title=العهد يعلن تعاقده مع نجم أردني|date=July 10, 2023|website=كووورة}}</ref> On 15 August 2024, Abu Hashish moved to [[Iraq Stars League]] club [[Zakho SC|Zakho]].<ref>{{cite web |last1=Mohammed |first1=Mustafa |title=زاخو يضم الأسود وأبو حشيش |url=https://www.kooora.com/?n=1348209 |website=Kooora.com |publisher=Kooora |language=Arabic |date=15 August 2024}}</ref> On 3 August 2025, Abu Hashish joined [[Al-Karma SC|Al-Karma]].<ref>{{cite web |title=الأردني "أبو حشيش" يدعم صفوف الكرمة |url=https://www.kooora.com/%D9%83%D8%B1%D8%A9-%D9%82%D8%AF%D9%85/%D8%A3%D8%AE%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%B1/%D8%A7%D9%94%D8%A8%D9%88-%D8%AD%D8%B4%D9%8A%D8%B4-%D9%8A%D8%AF%D8%B9%D9%85-%D8%B5%D9%81%D9%88%D9%81-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%83%D8%B1%D9%85%D8%A9/blt6134c92f2359e080 |website=kooora.com |publisher=Kooora |access-date=3 August 2025 |language=Arabic |date=3 August 2025}}</ref>

==International==
Eligible for Jordan and Iraq,<ref>{{cite web |title=الاردني محمد ابو حشيش يتحدث عن مشاعر والدته العراقية في مباراة العراق والاردن: "ستكون للوطن والابن".، |url=https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=8692531240860524 |website=facebook.com |publisher=Facebook |access-date=9 February 2025 |language=Arabic |date=9 November 2024}}</ref> Abu Hashish was first called up to the senior [[Jordan national football team|Jordan national team]] in a friendly 2–1 win over [[Bahrain national football team|Bahrain]] on 7 September 2021.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.national-football-teams.com/matches/report/31809/Bahrain_Jordan.html|title=Bahrain vs. Jordan|first=Benjamin|last=Strack-Zimmermann|website=www.national-football-teams.com}}</ref> He represented Jordan at the [[2021 FIFA Arab Cup]].<ref>{{Cite web|date=2021-11-26|title= رسميا.. حمد يعلن قائمة الأردن لكأس العرب |url=https://m.kooora.com/?n=1089782&o=ncjo|access-date=2021-11-26|website=كووورة.كوم|language=ar}}</ref> He was called up to the national team for the [[2023 AFC Asian Cup]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.kooora.com/?n=1294093|title=منتخب الأردن يستدعي أبو حشيش|date=December 19, 2023|website=كووورة}}</ref>

